        br
        .row
            .small-12.columns
                #top-logo
                    // Desktop Header
                    .hide-for-small
                        img.center(src="img/logo.svg", width="960px", alt="¡Sunset Spark!")
                            img.center(src="img/sunset-spark-trans-960x.png", alt="¡Sunset Spark!")

                    // Mobile Header
                    .row
                        .small-12.show-for-small.header-sml
                            img.center(src="img/logo.svg", width="610px", alt="¡Sunset Spark!")
                                img.center(src="img/sunset-spark-trans-610x.png", alt="¡Sunset Spark!")
        br

        .row
            .small-12.columns
                img.dna-hr(src="img/dna.png")
                br

        .row
            .small-12.columns
                .row
                    // About
                    .small-12.columns
                        .panel.radius
                            .row
                                .small-6.columns
                                    h2 Learning for Everyone
                                    hr
                                    p.
                                        Become an engineer, scientist, inventor and lifelong
                                        learner today.  Sunset Spark is a not-for-profit
                                        hackerspace for the immigrant community of Sunset Park.
                                        We offer free classes for kids and adults in a wide
                                        variety of science and engineering subjects like
                                        neuroscience, software engineering, and physical
                                        computing.
                                    p.
                                        We work with our students to make sure the classes meet
                                        their needs.  The best way to learn is to be engaged.
                                        All our classes have hands-on projects, experiments or
                                        immediate takeaways that will empower students of all ages
                                        to learn more on their own and use their new knowledge in
                                        the real world in creative and relevant ways.
                                    p.
                                        Our classes take place in borrow spaces like schools,
                                        parks and offices around Sunset Park.  We don't have a
                                        permanent home to call our own yet, but we're working
                                        toward opening a permanent location in the neighborhood
                                        soon to open up a technology workshop and offer more
                                        science and engineering classes to the community.

